body: "Npm publication is the only remaining release step. Local release gates, tarball artifact smoke, public GitHub pm install smoke, GitHub repository settings, and GitHub release v0.1.0 are complete. The actual npm publish attempt failed with ENEEDAUTH, and npm view still returns E404 for pm-changelog."
